{
  "text": "1) The physical \u03b2-functions for the classical cosmological constant a 6 , inverse Newton constant a 5 and for the coefficient q 1 of the non-local term \u03beK are not visible in this framework, for the reasons which were already explained above and in [CITATION_1] . Unfortunately, at this point there is no qualitative difference between the theory were the masses are introduced from the very beginning and the theory with SSB.",
